data.description: Call to preview this completely remodeled 4 bed 2 bath 2 story home just up from Lake Wales Lake in an established neighborhood and close to school, shopping, recreation and medical facilities. This home has too many updates to list here. There is also a detached building with AC and water that could easily be made into a 2-story mother-in-law suite/rental property with its own rear ally parking. Home boasts a great back yard for entertaining as well.
